==评价==
=== 专业评价 ===
汇总媒体[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据176条评论，给影片打出92%的新鲜度，平均得分7.8/10。网站共识写道：“加点导演得很灵巧的悲喜剧，加点陈年的托马斯·温特伯格元素，《酒精计划》这部让人有点上头的中年危机电影就这么来了<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/another_round|title=Another Round (2020)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|access-date=2021-03-27|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021083141/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/another_round|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据27条评论，打出81/100的平均分，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/another-round|title=Another Round Reviews|website=Metacritic|access-date=2021-03-15|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204231101/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/another-round|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

